originalText.text: The doorman is very rude. While leaving the store he checked my tiny purse which can just fit a small water bottle! He didn’t check my purse the week before that as I bought things from there! Also he was not checking white people’s purses!!!

originalText.text:
This is a place that discriminates against the disabled and senior citizens.. I was checking out....so far everyone seemed nice...then at check out there was an item marked with wrong price. I said how would I know what the price was.  I shared consumer law on pricing mistakes and then BOOM. DONT RAISE YOUR VOICE I WILL HAVE YOU REMOVED. I SAID I AM NOT RAISING MY  VOICE. AGAIN THE CLERK WITH LONG HAIR BELTS OUT...I WILL HAVE YOU REMOVED. I SAID...YOU ARE THE ONE ARGUING BECAUSE YOU MADE THE MISTAKE. THEN A NON SEQUITUR FOLLOWS....I DONT HAVE TO GIVE IT TO YOU AT THIS PRICE IF YOU CHANGED THE TAG. I SAID...ARE U ACCUSING ME OF CHANGING THE TAG. I SAID CHECK THE CAMERAS PLUS I COULDNT HAVE CHANGED THE TAG BECAUSE THE ITEM IS MARKED WITH A DESCRIPTION OF WHAT IT IS. THEN TO TRY TO GET THE ITEM BACK TO CORRECT THEIR MISTAKE....SHE BELTS OUT...I CAN JUST REFUND YOUR MONEY. I DONT WANT A REFUND I WANT THE ITEM. THEN SHE YELLS FOR A MALE EMPLOYEE TO THROW ME OUT. HE GRABS MY ARM. I SAID LET GO....CALL THE POLICE. LETS CHECK THE CAMERAS.....SEE RETAILERS NOW USE THIS EXCUSE...IF YOU RAISE YOUR VOICE WE CAN KICK YOU OUT. NOW HERE IT IS WITH COVID RUNNING RAMPID, WE ARE ALL WEARING MASKS AND THERE IS A PLASTIC BARRIER. BESIDES MY NOTICEABLE DISABILITY I ALSO CARRY A CARD. I SAID WAIT. YOU ARE MISUSING YOUR POWERS TO DISCRIMINATE. THEN THE OTHER SECURITY PEOPLE STARTED YELLING AT ME...LEAVE LEAVE...MAKING ME INTO A SCAPEGOAT FOR THEIR ERROR. AND THEY THINK THEY CAN GET AWAY WITH IT. WELL, FEDERAL LAW TRUMPS STUPIDITY!

WITH MY TRAINING I KNEW IMMEDIATELY TO START TAPING!!!!!
